  capistrano-2.5.18.ebuild:
  Unbreak ebuild by adding proper runtime dependencies, fixes bug #310115.

*capistrano-2.5.18 (16 Mar 2010)

  16 Mar 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +capistrano-2.5.18.ebuild:
  Version bump: fix for rolling back on local copy errors. Install VERSION
  file to make cap -V work.

