*capistrano-2.5.2 (17 Nov 2008)

  17 Nov 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +capistrano-2.5.2.ebuild:
  Version bump: Fix issue with git SCM that caused "Unable to resolve revision
  for 'HEAD'" errors on deploy. Also depend on rubygems 1.3.0 or better so that
  we don't need to have the development gems installed.

